PN,42501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FA 16-year-old who claimed to be a
OL,8,Fmember of a banned far-right
OL,9,Forganisation and who owned and shared
OL,10,Fterror publications has been detained
OL,11,Ffor three-and-a-half years.
OL,13,FThe Northumberland teenager, who
OL,14,Fcannot be identified for legal
OL,15,Freasons, must also serve a year's
OL,16,Fextended licence when released.
OL,18,FHe was convicted last month of five
OL,19,Fterror charges following a trial at
OL,20,FLeeds Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
