OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe jury was unable to agree a verdict
OL,8,Fon a charge that he was planning a
OL,9,Fterror attack on Newcastle synagogues
OL,10,Fand the prosecution said it would not
OL,11,Fapply for a retrial on that count.
OL,13,FJurors were told the teenager
OL,14,Fpurported to be a member of a
OL,15,Fproscribed neo-Nazi organisation, The
OL,16,FBase.
OL,18,FHe put stickers up promoting The Base,
OL,19,Fmade promotional material and
OL,20,Fencouraged others to join.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe boy's trial heard how police found
OL,8,Fan "arsenal" of weapons, including a
OL,9,Fcrossbow and knives, at his home in
OL,10,FNorthumberland in February 2025.
OL,12,FThe jury was shown images of his
OL,13,Fbedroom, including a replica of an SS
OL,14,Fofficer's cap, a flag of Rhodesia and
OL,15,Fa skeleton in a mask.
OL,17,FJurors were also read online exchanges
OL,18,Fthe teenager had with members of white
OL,19,Fsupremacist groups and violent journal
OL,20,Fentries.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe court was told that the youth
OL,8,Fwatched a video of the New Zealand
OL,9,Fmosque terror attack then looked up
OL,10,Fsynagogues in the Newcastle area.
OL,12,FHe also made racist and offensive
OL,13,Freferences in his journal, later
OL,14,Ftelling the jury he did not believe
OL,15,Fthem but he wrote them down to bring
OL,16,Fhimself peace.
OL,18,FMr Justice Wall, sentencing, said he
OL,19,Frejected that claim, saying the
OL,20,Fteenager genuinely held extremist,
OL,21,Fantisemitic views.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe judge did accept that the build-up
OL,8,Fto the offending began when the boy
OL,9,Fwas just 14, with most of them
OL,10,Fhappening when he was 15.
OL,12,FHe experienced a difficult childhood,
OL,13,Fsuffered from bullying, was isolated
OL,14,Fand struggled with friendships.
OL,16,FMr Justice Wall said the teenager must
OL,17,Fspend another 15 months in detention,
OL,18,Fhaving already been in custody since
OL,19,Fhis arrest.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FHe will then be supervised and
OL,8,Fmonitored in the community for another
OL,9,F26 months.
OL,11,FMr Justice Wall said the boy had an
OL,12,F"unhealthy interest in weapons, wars
OL,13,Fand paramilitary items and this
OL,14,Fobsession led you to exploring the
OL,15,Fdarker world of extreme right-wing
OL,16,Forganisations".
OL,18,FHe will be subject to a Criminal
OL,19,FBehaviour Order which will restrict
OL,20,Fhis use of computers and the internet.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FDuring the trial, Frida Hussain KC,
OL,8,Fdefending, said the boy was
OL,9,F"desperately lonely", had been
OL,10,F"plagued" with thoughts of killing
OL,11,Fhimself, and created an online persona
OL,12,Fas a distraction.
OL,14,FDetective Chief Superintendent James
OL,15,FDunkerley, Head of Counter Terrorism
OL,16,FPolicing North East, said: "We welcome
OL,17,Fthe sentence handed down today and
OL,18,Fhope it acts as a warning to all about
OL,19,Fthe dangers of extreme online content
OL,20,Fwhich can have real life consequences."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@TO]rD@AOUrD@IO]xD@\OU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FHe added: "If you are worried about
OL,8,Fsomeone you know expressing extreme
OL,9,Fviews or hatred, then please trust
OL,10,Fyour instincts and act early to
OL,11,Fprevent people becoming involved in
OL,12,Fterrorism. I cannot stress that enough
OL,13,Fand you will not be wasting our time."
OL,15,FChief Superintendent Kevin Waring,
OL,16,Farea commander for Northumberland,
OL,17,Fsaid: "This case highlights the
OL,18,Fdangers which exist online and the
OL,19,Ftype of material young people can
OL,20,Faccess.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@fO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1774890348
OL,3,C16-year-old from Northumberland
OL,4,Csentenced for right-wing terror
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,F"It is a reminder that we all need to
OL,8,Fbe vigilant and if you do become
OL,9,Fworried about someone you know, see or
OL,10,Fhear something concerning then please
OL,11,Fcome forward."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]
